sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant S as SecurityConfig
  participant K as Keycloak Adapter
  participant T as HttpTenantFilter
  participant R as TenantResolverService
  participant Ctrl as Controller
  C->>S: HTTP request + bearer token + CSRF when required
  S->>K: Validate bearer token and map roles
  S->>S: Match endpoint authority rules
  S->>T: Continue when multitenancy enabled
  T->>R: Resolve tenant from token/header/subdomain
  R-->>T: tenantId
  T->>Ctrl: Request with TenantContext
